data.description: SELLER is Ready to sell!!! Take a look at this well-maintained home on 7.69 acres in Glenwood. Three bedrooms and two bath with heated floor in both bathrooms. Has engineered floors and tile floors.  A large bright kitchen w/ plenty of room and cabinets. There is wood stove in the living room for those cold winter nights. large back deck with a screen in room on the back of the home. A great yard for kids to run and play or just sit in under the stars.
